synthesizer.content:
Given the following question and the following set of answers collected from clinical notes, synthesize the information into a single clinical variable. Describe the variable as a valid JSON using the following template. The clinical variable can be boolean, numeric (e.g., measurements) or categorical. For categorical variables, you must use 10 values at maximum.The type must be inferred from the question and the provided answers. The JSON content must be in Italian.
{{
  "Name": "field name",
  "Description": "This field is about...",
  "Type": "Categorical",
  "Values": ["value1", "value2", "value3"]
}}

history_consolidation.content:
